---
interface Props {
  /** Render as a bordered box (default) or plain inline text. */
  boxed?: boolean;
  class?: string;
}
const { boxed = true, class: className = '' } = Astro.props;
---

<aside
  class:list={[
    'text-xs text-text-muted leading-relaxed',
    boxed && 'border border-border bg-surface-dark p-4',
    className,
  ]}
>
  <span class="font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-text-muted">Note —</span>
  Inclusion does not imply guilt, wrongdoing, or criminal conduct of any kind. Many individuals
  appear only in passing, in routine correspondence, or because they are mentioned in news articles
  and links shared with or about Epstein. Each profile specifies the nature and context of the
  connection based on publicly available documents.
</aside>
